---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE, t } from '../../../data/i18n.js';
const lang = 'en';
---
<Base lang={lang} title="Guided Tour of Cuelgamuros — Book with María Victoria Solaz" description="Guided tour of Cuelgamuros (Valley of the Fallen). Rigorous historical context." path="/cuelgamuros/guided-tour/">
  <div class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 overflow-hidden">
    <img src="/img/cuelgamuros/atardecer-aerea.webp" alt="Cuelgamuros at sunset" class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Guided Tour</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-sepia mb-8">Cuelgamuros — Valley of the Fallen</p>
    <section class="mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Duration</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">Flexible</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Price</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">On request</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Languages</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">EN · ES · IT · FR · PT</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>A contextualised visit: the exterior, the rock-hewn basilica, the Spanish Civil War, the 2019 exhumations, and the current memory debate.</p>
        <p>For anyone who wants to understand this complex site. Combines with El Escorial — 10 km away.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="cta-green rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Book your tour</h2>
      <p class="text-sepia mb-4">Contact María Victoria directly</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34659953930?text=Hello%20María%20Victoria%2C%20I'd%20like%20a%20tour%20of%20Cuelgamuros" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block btn-whatsapp px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium">💬 WhatsApp</a>
      <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70 mt-4">Usually replies within 24 hours</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
